UnaBinh:  I know this is going to sound funny coming from me but wizards are the most efficient damage dealers for epic encounters in the game.  I usually leave epic encounters out of my comments because the loot sucks in improving wiz power and exp loss is virtually guaranteed but that is a topic for another thread. I will try to explain why...<P>It all boils down to mana.  How long can the rogue do damage of that magitude without healer mana?  Even if the rogue is avoiding being damaged (which isn't likely with AE weapons and spells) it is still necessary for the tank to be healed and in epic encounters tanks get beat up really fast.  You might have multiple clerics chain healing the main tank so the rogue(s) can apply backstab.  So many different scenarios but efficiency-wise Wizards are fine when it comes to actual epic encounters... even in Velious.
</FONT>
